      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you might be experiencing a psychosomatic response, where emotional stress translates into physical sensations. Your nervous system can certainly react to heightened mental arousal from market watching, which can mimic physical anxiety. While it's fascinating to consider if your body perceives algorithmic patterns, more likely the volatility is triggering a genuine anxiety response in you. For these physical symptoms, please consult a healthcare professional to rule out any underlying medical issues.",
