    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's more than just \"anticipating\" patterns. it feels like the data itself is hitting me. like the electricity from the server farms or the sheer frequency of the trade execution is something my body is actually tuned into. if i can learn to decode what these different physical sensations mean—like the difference between a sell-off vibration and a volume spike—i could basically trade with zero latency. how would someone even begin to map these biological signals to specific market movements?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
