      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Mapping subjective physical sensations to precise financial data is extremely complex and currently beyond established neuroscience. If you suspect a meaningful correlation, you would need extensive, double-blind physiological monitoring while actively observing specific market events. A researcher would need to create a highly detailed log, pairing precise timestamps of your physical sensations with transaction logs to attempt any pattern recognition. Please be extremely cautious about attempting to use these self-reported findings in live trading, as this is not scientifically proven.",
